data.description: Nestled on a generous half-acre lot, this cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home has recently been given a fresh update with new flooring, a splash of paint, and shiny new appliances. The inviting living room is anchored by a snug fireplace, perfect for those occasional chilly Georgia evenings. Outside, a screened-in back porch offers a peaceful spot to enjoy your morning coffee while taking in the view of the spacious fenced backyard. And don't forget the detached 2-car garage, providing plenty of storage space and convenience. It's the perfect blend of comfort and functionality for everyday living. Schedule your showing today!
